  "texts": [
    "We start with a warm-up period of 500 trading days for our estimators leaving us with 5,686 trading days, or approximately 22 years of data.",
    "The first 1,250 trading days (five years) are used to initialize the priority parameters.",
    "This leaves us with 4,436 out-of-sample trading days, approximately 17 years.",
    "Starting with an initial cash allocation of $1,000,000, we call the portfolio construction method each day to obtain the target weights.",
    "We then execute the trades at the closing price, rebalancing the portfolio to the new target weights, taking into account the weight changes due to the returns from the previous day."
  ],
